title: DEFENSE OF MINAS ITHIL - Third Age Total War Gameplay
description:
Third Age Total War Gameplay - The year is 2002 Third Age and the Witch King is marching a great army to take Minas Ithil.  Harad, allies of Mordor, is attacking from the beach, and Gondor is going to hold aginst them at the outpost of Minas Ithil!  Enjoy tha Battle! :D
